Scott Eastwood -LRB- born Scott Clinton Reeves ; March 21 , 1986 -RRB- is an American actor , model , and professional skydiver .
He has appeared in the films Flags of Our Fathers -LRB- 2006 -RRB- , Gran Torino -LRB- 2008 -RRB- , Invictus -LRB- 2009 -RRB- , The Forger -LRB- 2012 -RRB- , Trouble with the Curve -LRB- 2012 -RRB- , Texas Chainsaw -LRB- 2013 -RRB- , Fury -LRB- 2014 -RRB- , The Perfect Wave -LRB- 2014 -RRB- , The Longest Ride -LRB- 2015 -RRB- , Mercury Plains -LRB- 2016 -RRB- , Suicide Squad -LRB- 2016 -RRB- , Snowden -LRB- 2016 -RRB- and The Fate of the Furious -LRB- 2017 -RRB- .
He has also been the model for the fragrance Cool Water by Davidoff .
He is the youngest son of Academy Award-winning actor-director Clint Eastwood and second youngest of Jacelyn Reeves .